name: Problem Solver (Video version) #24
description:
Music: Ali Ahmadpour

Sometimes you are millions of particles.
Problem Solver who can make way for all the puzzles inside and outside of himself. The main image in this work is a collage of a combination of a 3D character with a few human portrait shots and geometric shape. Thinking and contemplation inside and outside human beings has caused surprises. This person is able to control various dimensions, which will result in overcoming difficult obstacles and reaching development and maturity.
